 SG_ Reserved1 : 40|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  MCU
 SG_ CRC8 : 48|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  MCU

BO_ 0x202 MCU_Power: 8 MCU
 SG_ DC_Link_Voltage : 0|12@1+ (0.1,0) [0|800] "V"  VCU
 SG_ DC_Link_Current : 12|12@1- (0.1,0) [-600|600] "A"  VCU
 SG_ Motor_Power : 24|16@1+ (0.1,0) [-200|200] "kW"  VCU
 SG_ Reserved1 : 40|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  MCU
 SG_ CRC8 : 48|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  MCU

BO_ 0x203 MCU_Efficiency: 8 MCU
 SG_ Motor_Efficiency : 0|8@1+ (0.5,0) [0|100] "%"  VCU
 SG_ Inverter_Efficiency : 8|8@1+ (0.5,0) [0|100] "%"  VCU
