 SG_ IGBT_Temperature : 24|8@1+ (1,-40) [-40|215] "C"  VCU
 SG_ Reserved1 : 32|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  MCU
 SG_ CRC8 : 40|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  MCU

BO_ 0x204 MCU_Flags: 8 MCU
 SG_ Torque_Limit_Flag : 0|1@1+ (1,0) [0|1] ""  VCU
 SG_ Speed_Limit_Flag : 1|1@1+ (1,0) [0|1] ""  VCU
 SG_ Over_Temperature_Flag : 2|1@1+ (1,0) [0|1] ""  VCU
 SG_ Under_Voltage_Flag : 3|1@1+ (1,0) [0|1] ""  VCU
 SG_ Over_Current_Flag : 4|1@1+ (1,0) [0|1] ""  VCU
 SG_ Fault_Flag : 5|1@1+ (1,0) [0|1] ""  MCU
 SG_ Reserved1 : 6|2@1+ (1,0) [0|3] ""  MCU
 SG_ Reserved2 : 8|20@1+ (1,0) [0|1048575] ""  MCU
 SG_ Rolling_Counter : 28|4@1+ (1,0) [0|15] ""  MCU
 SG_ CRC8 : 32|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  MCU

BO_ 0x205 MCU_Diagnostics: 8 MCU
 SG_ Fault_Code : 0|16@1+ (1,0) [0|65535] ""  VCU
 SG_ Fault_Code_2 : 16|16@1+ (1,0) [0|65535] ""  VCU
 SG_ Warning_Code : 32|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  VCU
 SG_ Reserved1 : 40|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  MCU
 SG_ CRC8 : 48|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  MCU

BO_ 0x206 MCU_Counter: 8 MCU
 SG_ Odometer : 0|24@1+ (0.01,0) [0|100000] "km"  VCU
