 SG_ CRC8 : 40|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  BMS

BO_ 0x302 BMS_HV_Status: 8 BMS
 SG_ Pack_Voltage : 0|12@1+ (0.1,0) [0|800] "V"  VCU
