 SG_ CRC8 : 48|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  BMS

BO_ 0x303 BMS_Cell_Status: 8 BMS
 SG_ Cell_Max_Voltage : 0|12@1+ (0.001,0) [2.5|4.5] "V"  VCU
 SG_ Cell_Max_Index : 12|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  VCU
 SG_ Cell_Min_Voltage : 20|12@1+ (0.001,0) [2.5|4.5] "V"  VCU
 SG_ Cell_Min_Index : 32|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  VCU
 SG_ Reserved1 : 40|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  BMS
 SG_ CRC8 : 48|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  BMS

BO_ 0x304 BMS_Temperature: 8 BMS
 SG_ Pack_Max_Temp : 0|8@1+ (1,-40) [-40|215] "C"  VCU
