 SG_ Balancing_Current : 16|8@1+ (0.1,0) [0|5] "A"  VCU
 SG_ Balancing_Time : 24|16@1+ (1,0) [0|65535] "s"  VCU
 SG_ Reserved1 : 40|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] ""  BMS
